  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107040/extras/dab3b785cdae17dc45b097cf5e5f06fb.poster.avif?t=1750439562\" width=800 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107040/extras/dab3b785cdae17dc45b097cf5e5f06fb.webm?t=1750439562\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107040/extras/dab3b785cdae17dc45b097cf5e5f06fb.mp4?t=1750439562\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Step into a world of fear with a dark, twisted version of the classic word game 'Hangman' reimagined. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>From the creators of Greg's Deadly Draft</strong> comes a truly terrifying experience...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trapped in a cold storage room by a madman with murderous intent, you must solve your way out of the situation by correctly guessing words. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a subject that will lead you down a dangerous path. Supply power to the generator while simultaneously dealing with <strong>the Hangbuddy.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Hangbuddy</strong> was created to do everything in it's power to distract you from the task at hand, make sure to keep an eye out for what shenanigans it might cause...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107040/extras/dab3b785cdae17dc45b097cf5e5f06fb.poster.avif?t=1750439562\" width=800 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107040/extras/dab3b785cdae17dc45b097cf5e5f06fb.webm?t=1750439562\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107040/extras/dab3b785cdae17dc45b097cf5e5f06fb.mp4?t=1750439562\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Step into a world of fear with a dark, twisted version of the classic word game 'Hangman' reimagined. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>From the creators of Greg's Deadly Draft</strong> comes a truly terrifying experience...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trapped in a cold storage room by a madman with murderous intent, you must solve your way out of the situation by correctly guessing words. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a subject that will lead you down a dangerous path. Supply power to the generator while simultaneously dealing with <strong>the Hangbuddy.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Hangbuddy</strong> was created to do everything in it's power to distract you from the task at hand, make sure to keep an eye out for what shenanigans it might cause...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
